  <brief_title>How Neurofibromatosis Type 1 (NF1) Affects Schoolwork and Self-Esteem</brief_title>
  <official_title>Cognitive Impairments, Self-Esteem &amp; Academic Performance in Teenagers With Neurofibromatosis Type 1</official_title>
