  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study will seek to determine whether there is a corresponding deficit in school
      performance for teenagers with NF1. Secondly, the study seeks to explore the issue of
      self-esteem in teenagers with NF1.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
